Description:
You meet a young girl with a strange duck, next to them there are several monsters but they seem harmless, when you approach she says to you:

"Hello travellers, as you can see, I am a monster trainer and I have already tamed a few in this area, if you want you can keep them in exchange for a small favour. 

I would need you to take this monster egg to a friend of mine called Bash, I think he is somewhere in the upper ruins."
DescriptionAction: Do you want to help the girl?
